item.title: CVE-2023-29185|2024-08-02T14:00:15.869Z -- sap -- netweaver%20as%20for%20abap%20%28business%20server%20pages%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS for ABAP (Business Server Pages) - versions 700, 701, 702, 731, 740, 750, 751, 752, 753, 754, 755, 756, 757, allows an attacker authenticated as a non-administrative user to craft a request with certain parameters in certain circumstances which can consume the server's resources sufficiently to make it unavailable over the network without any user interaction.
